ly believe they committed fraud. There=E2=80=99s no other way to state it: =
That=E2=80=99s fraud =E2=80=94 they lied,=E2=80=9D Lane Kasselman, chief bu=
siness officer of blockchain.com, told me after Three Arrows Capital filed =
