e end. =E2=80=9CThere are not. Why are there not? There are not for a reaso=
n: Because we did not.=E2=80=9D
And also their plans for the future, which started with OPNX, which was sup=
posed to be an exchange for trading crypto bankruptcy claims (an incredible=
