e =E2=80=94 one they were calling OX.Fun. But this time they would not trad=
e creditor claims but rather crypto tokens. So far, the tokens they=E2=80=
=99ve announced are of the exchange=E2=80=99s own making with names like OX=
 and Milk and Autism. =E2=80=9C$OX is an ecosystem, economy, community,=E2=
=80=9D Davies wrote on X after OPNX announced it would shut down. Zhu later=
 elaborated: =E2=80=9COx.fun is a revolutionary new design for gamified per=
ps trading, collat and profit/loss are entirely in OX, you earn high yields=
 for completing missions, and you earn MILK when you realise losses.=E2=80=
=9D=C2=A0
=E2=80=9CIf this reads like nonsense to you, you are not alone,=E2=80=9D wr=
ites Wieczner, but that's the point! It=E2=80=99s not=C2=A0lies, it=E2=80=
=99s=C2=A0nonsense. The pitch is that you can trade nonsense, in a =E2=80=
=9Cgamified=E2=80=9D way, and earn more nonsense when you lose money on you=
r nonsense trading. It=E2=80=99s =E2=80=9Chey, if you want to blow your mon=
ey on something dumb, we=E2=80=99ve got something dumb for you.=E2=80=9D Th=
at has worked for them before!

