blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bo=
ttom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; =
background-color: #ccc;">SEC rules</a> require companies that own more than=
 $100 million worth of publicly traded stock to file Form 13F, beginning th=
