<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Also it=E2=80=99s worth pointing out that =E2=
=80=9C13F day=E2=80=9D is a thing: Most 13F filers file right at the quarte=
rly deadline, many 13F filers are prominent investors (hedge fund managers,=
 Warren Buffett, Cathie Wood), and people pay=C2=A0attention=C2=A0to their =
filings. Journalists write up the stocks that they have bought and sold, th=
ose stories get a lot of readers, and other investors sometimes copy their =
moves. A 13F disclosing that a celebrity investor bought a small stock=C2=
=A0in December can cause that stock to rally in February.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">So if you were familiar with Arm=E2=80=99s IPO=
 prospectus, and the SEC=E2=80=99s ownership disclosure rules, and seven ye=
