=99s reporting=C2=A0of 13F filings, and the popular=C2=A0interest=C2=A0that=
 makes Nvidia=E2=80=99s moves worth following,=C2=A0you could have formed t=
he following thesis last month:</p>
<ol style=3D"list-style-type: decimal; padding-left: 40px; margin: 16px 0;"=
>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">Nvidia probably owns stakes in SoundH=
ound and Nano-X.</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">It will probably =
